[[File:BankOfJabba.jpg|thumb|The Bank of Jabba.]]
The '''Bank of Jabba''' was a novelty coin bank in the shape of [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba Desilijic Tiure]] that he had received from a [[Merchant/Legends|merchant]]. Jabba had the merchant put to [[Death/Legends|death]] soon after. Following Jabba's death, [[Gorga Desilijic Aarrpo/Legends|Gorga Desilijic Aarrpo]] received "entire holdings" of the bank, which he was most disappointed by.<ref name="TJT">"[[The Jabba Tape]]"</ref>

